TextBox.Value: 1.All service charges are Cash-On Delivery.#010;2.Any cancellation of repair service for over warranty & warranty void cases, minimum RM60.00 cancellation fees will be imposed. Vendor's cancellation charges apply accordingly.#010;3.A NON-REFUNDABLE deposit of RM60.00 which is payable by Cash or Credit Card, for the repair cost to be paid upfront when send to Highpoint Service Network Sdn. Bhd. In the event that the customer decides to cancel the repair, the RM60.00 non-refundable deposit will be used as inspection fees and/or disposal.#010;4.In keeping with the Personal Data Protection Act, we encourage users to back up all data before sending your faulty unit to Highpoint for repairs. Kindly note that Highpoint will not be held responsible for any data loss in the course of carrying out the necessary repairs.#010;5.We hereby authorized Highpoint to reformat the HDD if necessary and accept that there will be data loss from reformatting.#010;6.Should any machine, in which repair/cancel of service has been completed for more that 7 (seven) days be uncollected by the customer and continues to be left in the premises of Highpoint even though Highpoint has notified the customer to collect, then Highpoint may at its complete discretion, sell, dispose off or handle the machine in any way it deems fit. Highpoint reserve the right to apply the proceeds of any sale to offset the costs incurred in the repair or services of the machine as well as any other incidental expenses.#010;7.If Acer repaired products have the same problem within 90 days after date of collection, there will be no charge for further repair. If different malfunction occurs, it will be treated as a new case. For other repaired products, principal’s T&C applied accordingly#010;8.All Part(s) replaced, the faulty part(s) shall become the property of Highpoint Service Network.#010;9.Unless requested, equipment collected for repair is not verified by drivers at pick-up point. Highpoint reserve the right to inform customers of any damage or missing parts within next business day.#010;10.For out of warranty printer repairs, warranty for labour is one (1) month while spare part carries vendor warranty.
